,{"type":"entry","text":"nil","headword":"nil"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.无，零（nothing.zero)"},{"type":"text","text":"[nxl]"},{"type":"text","text":"圈词根记忆：ni（看作ne，无，没有）+l→无，零"},{"type":"entry","text":"abase","headword":"abase"},{"type":"definition","text":"v降低-的地位，贬抑，使卑下(to lower oneself or sb. in dignity; degrade oneself"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'bers]"},{"type":"text","text":"or sb.)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：a（表加强）+base（低，下）→往低压（自己）→降低的地位"},{"type":"entry","text":"infatuate","headword":"infatuate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使迷恋(to inspire with a foolish or extravagant love or admiration)：使期涂(to"},{"type":"text","text":"[rn'fatfuert]"},{"type":"text","text":"cause to deprive of sound judgment)"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：in（进入）+fatu（笨）+ale→因迷恋而变笨→使糊涂"},{"type":"entry","text":"nomad","headword":"nomad"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.流浪者（any wanderer)：游牧部落的人"},{"type":"text","text":"traverse"},{"type":"text","text":"['naumaed]"},{"type":"text","text":"国联想记忆：no+mad（疯狂的）→流浪者不疯也狂→流浪者"},{"type":"entry","text":"traverse","headword":"traverse"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.横穿，横跨（to go or travel across or over)"},{"type":"text","text":"[tra'v3:rs]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：tra（穿过）+vers（转向）+e→横穿，横跨"},{"type":"entry","text":"gist","headword":"gist"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.要点，要旨（the essence or main point)"},{"type":"text","text":"[d3rst]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：list(列出）the gists（要点）"},{"type":"text","text":"Peter has a bad habit of making dligressive remarks"},{"type":"text","text":"that cause us to forget the gist of what he is saying."},{"type":"entry","text":"implore","headword":"implore"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.哀求，悬求（to beg)"},{"type":"text","text":"[xm'plo:r]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：im（进入）+plor（哭泣）+e→哭泣→哀求"},{"type":"entry","text":"confess","headword":"confess"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.承认，供认(to admit that one has done wrong)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kan'fes]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：con（加强）+fess（说）→全部说