itate, nettle, rile, vex"},{"type":"entry","text":"incogitant","headword":"incogitant"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj未经思考的，考虑不周的(thoughtlessinconsiderate)"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：in（不）+co（共同）+g（看作ag，开动）+it+ant→不开动脑筋的→未经思"},{"type":"text","text":"[n'ka:d3rtant]"},{"type":"text","text":"考的"},{"type":"entry","text":"anneal","headword":"anneal"},{"type":"text","text":".使（金属、玻璃等）退火；使加强，使变硬（to strengthen orharden）"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'ni:l]"}]},{"number":293,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"disinter","headword":"disinter"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 挖出, 签出(to unearth; remove from a grave, tomb)"},{"type":"text","text":"[drsin't3:r]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：dis（除去）+inter（埋葬）→把埋葬的（东西）提出→挖出"},{"type":"entry","text":"scurvy","headword":"scurvy"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj卑都的，下流的（despicable)"},{"type":"text","text":"['sks:rvi]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆不要和scurry（v急跑，疾行）相混"},{"type":"entry","text":"vouch","headword":"vouch"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 担保，保证(to guarantee the reliability of)"},{"type":"text","text":"[vaut]"},{"type":"text","text":"1 can vouch for his honesty: I have always found him veracious and carefully"},{"type":"text","text":"observant of the truth."},{"type":"entry","text":"wheedle","headword":"wheedle"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 哄骗,诱骗(to influence or entice by soft words or flaltery)"},{"type":"text","text":"['wi:dl]"},{"type":"text","text":"cajole, coax, seduce"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.(船)倾斜(to lean sideways);使倾斜(to cause a ship to lean)"},{"type":"entry","text":"careen","headword":"careen"},{"type":"text","text":"[ka'riin]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：船倾斜（careen）了，但船家并不在意（care）"},{"type":"entry","text":"effulgent","headword":"effulgent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj 灿兰的，光辉的(of great brightness)"},{"type":"text","text":"[r'fAldsant]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：ef（出）+fulg（发光）+ent→发出光→灿烂的"},{"type":"entry","text":"bribe","headword":"bribe"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 贿略(to induce or influence by bribery)"},{"type":"text","text":"[brarb]"},{"type":"definition","text":"v 积聚(to collect; gather; accumulate)"},{"type":"entry","text":"amass","headword":"amass"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'maes]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：a（表加强）+mass（聚集）→积聚"},{"type":"entry","text":"carouse","headword":"carouse"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.狂饮寻乐(a noisy, merry drinking party)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ka'rauz]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：car+（r)ouse（唤起）→开着汽车欢闹→狂饮寻乐"},{"type":"entry","text":"dally","headword":"dally"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.闲荡，嬉戏(to waste time; loiter; trifle)"},{"type":"text","text":"['daeli]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：和daily（adj每日的）一起记"},{"type":"entry","text":"homely","headword":"homely"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 朴素的(simple and unpretentious);不漂亮的(plain or unattractive)"},{"type":"text","text":"['haumli]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：home（家）+ly→家庭用的→朴素的"},{"type":"entry","text":"debark","headword":"debark"},{"type":"definition","text":"V下船，下飞机，下车；卸载（客、货）"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'ba:rk]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：de(下)+bark(船)→下船"},{"type":"entry","text":"heckle","headword":"heckle"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 话问], 责问](to annoy or harass by interrupting with questions or taunts)"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：he（他）+ckle（看作buckle，扣上）→他因无故把人扣住不放受到洁问→"},{"type":"text","text":"['hekl]"},{"type":"text","text":"请问"},{"type":"entry","text":"demonstrative","headword":"demonstrative"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj证明的，论证的（demonstrating as real or true)：感情流露的（showing the"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'ma:nstratrv]"},{"type":"text","text":"feelings readily)"},{"type":"text","text":"snarl"},{"type":"entry","text":"snarl","headword":"snarl"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.纠缠，混乱(to intertwine;tangle);咆哮，怒骂(to"},{"type":"text","text":"[snairl]"},{"type":"text","text":"growi)n.纠缠，混乱；怒吼声，咆哮声"},{"type":"text","text":"knot"},{"type":"entry","text":"compress","headword":"compress"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 压缩;压紧(to press together; contract)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kam'pres]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：com（加强）+press（压）→压缩"},{"type":"entry","text":"tangy","headword":"tangy"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 气味刺激的,扑鼻的(having a pleasantly sharp flavor)"},{"type":"text","text":"['tani]"},{"type":"entry","text":"acrid","headword":"acrid"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 辛辣的，刻满的(bitterly pungent; bitter; sharp)"}]},{"number":294,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 25 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"pittance","headword":"pittance"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.微薄的薪俸，少量的收入（a meager monetary allowance，wage，or"},{"type":"text","text":"['prtns]"},{"type":"text","text":"remuneration) ; 少量(a very small amount)"},{"type":"entry","text":"nadir","headword":"nadir"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 最低点(the lowest point)"},{"type":"text","text":"['nerdrr]"},{"type":"text","text":"the nadir of one’s career某人事业上的低谷"},{"type":"entry","text":"lustrous","headword":"lustrous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 有光泽的(having luster; bright)"},{"type":"text","text":"[lAstras]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自luster（n.光辉；光泽）"},{"type":"entry","text":"ooze","headword":"ooze"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.慢慢地流，渗出（toleakout slowly)：（勇气）逐渐消失"},{"type":"text","text":"[u:z]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：oo（像水渗出来时冒的泡泡）+ze→渗出"},{"type":"entry","text":"dawdle","headword":"dawdle"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.闲荡，虚度光阴(to waste time in trifing: idlle; loiter)"},{"type":"text","text":"['d:d]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：daw（n)（黎明）+dle→漫无目的地游荡到黎明→闲荡"},{"type":"entry","text":"malaise","headword":"malaise"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 不适，不舒服(a feeling of illness)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ma’lerz]"},{"type":"entry","text":"protuberant","headword":"protuberant"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj突出的，隆起的（thrusting out:prominent)"},{"type":"text","text":"[prau'tu:barant]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：pro（向前）+tuber（块茎）+ant→像块茎一样突出的→突出的"},{"type":"entry","text":"nettle","headword":"nettle"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.尊麻v烦忧，激怒（to irritate:provoke)"},{"type":"text","text":"['netl]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：用nettle（尊麻）织网（net）"},{"type":"entry","text":"wallow","headword":"wallow"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 打溶(to roll the body about in or as if in water, snow, or mud) : 沉遗(to take"},{"type":"text","text":"[wa:lau]"},{"type":"text","text":"unrestrained pleasure) n. J演(the act or an instance of wallowing)"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：wal（看作wall，墙）+low（地势低的）→在墙底下打滚→打滚"},{"type":"entry","text":"persecute","headword":"persecute"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 追割(to oppress or harass with ill treatment)"},{"type":"text","text":"['p3:rsikju:t]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：per（加强）+secut（跟随）+e→跟在后面（坏你的事）→迫害"},{"type":"entry","text":"peremptory","headword":"peremptory"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj不容反抗的：专横的（masterful)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pa'remptari]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：per(加强）+empt（拿）+ory→全部拿走的→专横的"},{"type":"entry","text":"aspirant","headword":"aspirant"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 有抱负者(a person who aspires after honors or high positions)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'spararant]"},{"type":"entry","text":"aspirer","headword":"aspirer"},{"type":"entry","text":"merited","headword":"merited"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.该得的，理所当然的（deserving，worthy of)"},{"type":"text","text":"['merrtid]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：merit（价值）+ed→值得的→该得的"},{"type":"entry","text":"gourmand","headword":"gourmand"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 嘴食者(a person who indulges in food and drink, glutton)"},{"type":"text","text":"['gurma:nd]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：g（看作go，去）+our+man+d→我们的人都爱去吃各种美食→嗜食者"},{"type":"entry","text":"agog","headword":"agog"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.兴奋的，有强烈兴趣的(in a state of eager anticipation or excitement)"},{"type":"text","text":"agog可以作词根，意为“引导”，如demagog（n.编动者）"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'ga:g]"}]},{"number":295,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"delusion","h